{"tid":1498983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"幫港鐵申請臨時禁制令嘅係余若海","createTime":"2019-08-23T14:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T15:02:33.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0842075c84041cc2a475a7e95c0c23550fb12f9d","tid":1498983,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"相反佢家姐余若薇就同老公 去咗銅鑼灣手拖手組人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OFq5O0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OFq5O0.jpg&h=97f7721d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，批機場禁制令同港鐵禁制令嘅係同一個官<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>港鐵今午傳出消息，指將就示威者於港鐵站內的行為採取法律行動，包括申請禁制令，至晚上約9時，律師團隊陸逐現身高等法院，有關聆訊由日前批出機場禁制令的法官周家明審理，法官下令有關聆訊不對外公開，傳媒亦無法入內旁聽。<br />\n<br />\n負責處理申請的資深大律師余若海，於晚上約9時半到庭，聆訊歷時僅8分鐘便完結。據了解，法官<span style=\"color: red;\">即時批出</span>有關臨時禁制令，有效期至下星期五，即8月30日，而禁制令覆蓋範圍則尚待港鐵公佈，禁制令將規範<span style=\"color: red;\">3種不同的行為</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2434717/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2434717%2F&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=d8c3d893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2434717/</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c29a6f7827e624b16916931c582883d2d7df8e3a","tid":1498983,"uid":38432,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVu0ah6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVu0ah6.jpg&h=042d702e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a49e01b47e6b7bae7e81b846b82a6eb07c9cb8c","tid":1498983,"uid":219470,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:45:56.000Z","msg":"cab rank rule<br />\n大律師無得揀客"},{"pid":"a997907df3072efeb4ddbdfb055ec10330fe5c8f","tid":1498983,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"兩姊弟真心各走唔同路<img src=\"/asset